OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few bright
OL,6,For sunny spells this evening across
OL,7,Feastern counties, however thicker,
OL,8,Flower cloud already across Devon and
OL,9,FCornwall will become more widespread
OL,10,Fovernight, with some patchy drizzle
OL,11,Fdeveloping later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FRather cloudy on Wednesday
OL,14,Fwith further outbreaks of mostly light
OL,15,Fdrizzle, mainly across the hills and
OL,16,Fmoors. A more organised band of rain
OL,17,Farriving from the northwest in the
OL,18,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
