OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FCloud
OL,6,Fclearing early on Thursday, then fine
OL,7,Fwith some sunshine. Turning unsettled
OL,8,Fover the Easter weekend with showers
OL,9,For longer spells of rain. Some strong
OL,10,Fand gusty winds too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
